*
* AppCSXCAD - Minimal Application using the QCSXCAD library
*

AppCSXCAD is a minimal application using the QCSXCAD library, and AppCSXCAD-rs is the fork rewrite in rust.
AppCSXCAD is licensed under the terms of the GPLv3, which is permitted to copy and distribute verbatim copies of this license document, but changing it is not allowed.
